A React project with Firebase.
Utilized Firebase's email and password authentication.
Implemented React Context API to be able to access the user from anywhere. (much more effecient than prop drilling)
User is able to see their email in the navbar when they sign in by creating a Data Layer. 
User is able to add to their cart when they click on the product's button. 
Utilized CurrencyFormat from react-currency-format to automatically upadate the price total in the cart. 
Utilized Stripe API. 
